### Create a station (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Semenggoh Nature Reserve"
}

###

### List all stations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a station
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update a station
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Semenggoh Wildlife Centre"
}

###

### Delete a station (blocked if guides are assigned)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stations/{{stationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
